{\n  "title": "Implement Draft Iteration Mode Feature",\n  "body": "Enable a \"Draft Iteration Mode\" for enhanced content generation. Instead of a one-shot generation, this mode will allow users to iteratively refine content by providing feedback. Examples of potential user prompts for iteration could include:\n  - “Make the intro more engaging”\n  - “Add more technical depth to section 3”\n  - “This sounds too formal, make it more like my other posts”\n\nAdditional Feature:\n- Track revision history with diff views to show changes made during the refinement process."\n}